{"tid":2244840,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何志平同意向拜登支付100萬美元聘用“法律顧問”  拜登律師：不回應 /拜登仔同中國華信做過千萬生意","createTime":"2020-10-15T19:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T02:06:48.000Z","uid":47352,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"aadc65c0f2192fc48f5a0c4e8198c52c1114b635","tid":2244840,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T19:11:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://nypost.com/2020/10/15/emails-reveal-how-hunter-biden-tried-to-cash-in-big-with-chinese-firm/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2020%2F10%2F15%2Femails-reveal-how-hunter-biden-tried-to-cash-in-big-with-chinese-firm%2F&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=108adb6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://nypost.com/2020/10/15/emails-reveal-how-hunter-biden-tried-to-cash-in-big-with-chinese-firm/</a><br />\n<br />\ngoogletranslate<br />\n獲得的文件還包括2017年9月簽署的&ldquo;律師聘書&rdquo;，葉中的一名中尉，前香港政府官員（何志平）同意向拜登支付100萬美元的聘用&ldquo;法律顧問&rdquo;有關任何美國律師事務所或律師的僱用和法律分析的美國法律和建議。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n2018年12月，曼哈頓聯邦陪審團判處何浩有兩個計劃，以賄賂非洲高級政府官員300萬美元，以獲取乍得的石油權利和烏干達的豐厚商業交易。<br />\n<br />\n放大圖片<br />\n通過電子郵件發送有關協議的信息<br />\n<br />\n何先生被判處三年徒刑，並於六月被驅逐回香港。<br />\n<br />\n拜登的律師，喬&middot;拜登（Joe Biden）競選活動，吉利亞（Gilliar），董（Dong）和何（Ho）的律師均未回復置評請求，但拜登的律師此前曾表示：&ldquo;無需對Rudy Giuliani提供的任何所謂信息發表評論。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;他一直在公開推崇關於拜登家族的陰謀論，公開依靠與俄羅斯情報有聯繫的演員。他在這些問題上的不誠實記錄是不言而喻的。&rdquo;律師喬治&middot;梅西雷斯（George Mesires）補充說。<br />\n<br />\n魯汶&middot;芬頓（Rouven Fenton）的補充報導"},{"pid":"24aa2541cf19e874f5cfcfdbab91d01994465ac9","tid":2244840,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T19:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210259ac1be6366fb5b2404cd80150cecf449991","tid":2244840,"uid":1643,"like":27,"dis